---
// Full-width contact call-to-action strip
---

<section class="relative border-t border-primary bg-secondary py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-family-heading)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
      Available for permanent roles and long-term contracts.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/70 mb-3 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      I'm based in Brisbane and available for embedded architecture and delivery roles across Australia.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white/50 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm">
      Also open to independent consulting and architecture engagements.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="mailto:contact@movetodigital.au"
        class="inline-block bg-primary text-white rounded-lg px-8 py-3 font-medium transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-primary-dark hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/20"
      >
        contact@movetodigital.au
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kevinsee-au/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block border border-white/30 text-white/80 rounded-lg px-8 py-3 font-medium transition-all duration-200 hover:border-white/60 hover:text-white"
      >
        View LinkedIn Profile
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
